means: 没有知觉，不在乎，不关心

sentence.Network_en: He showed total insensibility to the animal's fate.

sentence.Network_en: His insensibility to art indicates that he will never become a real artist.
sentence.Network_cn: 他不会欣赏艺术,他将永远也成为不了一名真正的艺术家.
